<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,313,471,497]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Remarks.</emphasis>
This study reports the occurrence of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gmelin" authorityYear="1791" box="[757,902,472,497]" class="Gastropoda" family="Conidae" genus="Conus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Neogastropoda" pageId="50" pageNumber="51" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="violaceus">
<emphasis box="[757,902,472,497]" italics="true" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">C. violaceus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
for the first time from 
<collectingCountry box="[1179,1243,472,498]" name="India" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">India</collectingCountry>
